nter gap-8\"><a class=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-electric-blue border border-electric-blue/30 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full hover:bg-electric-blue hover:text-white transition-all animate-pulse\" href=\"/immersive\">Immersive Universe</a><div class=\"relative group\"><a class=\"text-sm font-medium text-foreground/80 hover:text-electric-blue transition-colors flex items-center gap-1 uppercase tracking-wider\" href=\"#services\">Services<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down transition-transform duration-200\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></a></div><div class=\"relative group\"><a class=\"text-sm font-medium text-foreground/80 hover:text-electric-blue transition-colors flex items-center gap-1 uppercase tracking-wider\" href=\"/training\">Training<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down transition-transform duration-200\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></a></div><div class=\"relative group\"><a class=\"text-sm font-medium text-foreground/80 hover:text-electric-blue transition-colors flex items-center gap-1 uppercase tracking-wider\" href=\"/resources\">Resources<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down transition-transform duration-200\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></a></div><div class=\"relative group\"><a class=\"text-sm font-medium text-foreground/80 hover:text-electric-blue transition-colors flex items-center gap-1 uppercase tracking-wider\" href=\"/portfolio\">Company<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down transition-transform duration-200\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></a></div><a class=\"bg-electric-blue text-white px-6 py-2 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider hover:bg-electric-blue-lt transition-colors rounded-sm\" href=\"/contact\">Get Started</a></div><button class=\"lg:hidden text-white\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></button></div></nav><main class=\"flex-grow\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-6 py-20 max-w-4xl\"><h1 class=\"text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6\">Untitled</h1><p class=\"text-gold mb-10\"></p><div class=\"prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none\"><p class=\"mb-4\">---\r</p><p class=\"mb-4\">title: &quot;Print Marketing Still Works in Nigeria: How to Use Banners, Flyers &amp; Business Cards&quot;\r</p><p class=\"mb-4\">date: &quot;2025-01-15T00:00:00Z&quot;\r</p><p class=\"mb-4\">description: &quot;Print isn&#x27;t dead in Nigeria. Learn how to strategically use flyers, banners, and cards to complement your digital marketing.&quot;\r</p><p class=\"mb-4\">---\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">Hephzibah Media\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">      - [Services](index.html#services)\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">      - [About](about.html)\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">      - [Landing Pages](landing-pages-sales-funnels.html)\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">      - [Training](training.html)\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">      - [Get a Quote](contact.html&quot; class=&quot;nav-cta)\r</p><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">      Print Marketing · 7 min read\r</p><p class=\"mb-4\">      # Print Marketing Still Works in Nigeria: 2025 Guide\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">      By Hephzibah Media Team · Published January 5, 2025\r</p><p class=\"mb-4\">      Everyone talks about &#x27;going digital.&#x27; But in Nigeria, print is still incredibly effective  especially when combined with digital. A high-quality business card at a networking event opens doors Google Ads can&#x27;t. A branded banner at a trade show generates qualified foot traffic. Here&#x27;s the strategic print playbook for 2025.\r</p><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">      ## Business Cards: Still Your Best Networking Tool\r</p><br/><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">A premium business card (embossed, foil-stamped, specialty paper) positions you as professional and established. It stays on a prospect&#x27;s desk for months. Cost: ?515 per card. Return: One client contract pays for 10,000 cards. Recommendation: 500 cards every 3 months.\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">      ## Flyers: Targeted Distribution Beats Broadcast\r</p><br/><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">Don&#x27;t print 10,000 flyers and hope. Instead: 500 flyers, hand-distributed at three high-traffic locations (office parks, malls, events) by your sales team. Include a QR code linking to a landing page  track clicks to measure ROI. Cost: ?50100 per flyer. Conversion: 25% is excellent for flyer campaigns.\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">      ## Banners at Trade Shows &amp; Events\r</p><br/><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">A trade show booth with a compelling banner, product samples, and a clear CTA (&#x27;Scan to get 20% off&#x27;) generates 1020 leads per day. Cost: ?20K50K for the banner. Value: One converted lead from an event is worth ?500K+. Attend 23 high-quality events yearly.\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">      ## Large Format Printing for Visibility\r</p><br/><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">A billboard for your agency costs ?200K500K monthly in high-traffic areas (Lekki, VI, GRA Ikeja). It&#x27;s expensive, but if your CAC (customer acquisition cost) is below ?50K, a billboard that generates 1015 leads monthly pays for itself. Best for services (real estate, education, fintech).\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">      ## Packaging as Marketing\r</p><br/><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">A branded box, tissue paper, or thank-you card in your order transforms a transaction into an experience. Customers photograph it for Instagram. Cost: ?100300 per order. Impact: Word-of-mouth multiplier of 23×.\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">      ## The Print + Digital Combo\r</p><br/><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">QR codes on every print piece. Flyers link to a landing page. Banners include a unique promo code. Business cards have a QR to your LinkedIn. Print gets attention; digital captures the lead. Together, they outperform either channel alone.\r</p><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">    ## Ready for Growth?\r</p><br/><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">Let our team audit your current marketing strategy and show you exactly what&#x27;s holding you back.\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">    [Start Your Free Audit](contact.html&quot; class=&quot;btn-primary)\r</p><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">        Hephzibah Media\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">Nigeria&#x27;s premium Digital Marketing, Tech &amp; Print Agency. Building brands that dominate from Ogere, Ogun State.\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">        Old Ode Road, Along Ogere Tollgate, Ogere, Nigeria\r</p><br/><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">        Services\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">          - [Web Design](web-design.html)\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">          - [Digital Marketing](digital-marketing.html)\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">          - [SEO](seo.html)\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">          - [Graphics Design](graphics-design.html)\r</p><br/><br/><br/><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">        Resources\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">          - [Blog](blog.html)\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">          - [Portfolio](portfolio.html)\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">          - [About Us](about.html)\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">          - [Contact](contact.html)\r</p><br/><br/><br/><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">        Connect\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">          - [WhatsApp](https://wa.me/2349077780156)\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">          - [Email](mailto:hello@hephzibahmedia.com.ng)\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">          - [Instagram](https://instagram.com/hephzibahmedia&quot; rel=&quot;noopener)\r</p><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">          - [LinkedIn](https://linkedin.com/company/hephzibahmedia&quot; rel=&quot;noopener)\r</p><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><p class=\"mb-4\">      © 2026 Hephzibah Media. All rights reserved.\r</p><p class=\"mb-4\">      Built for speed. Engineered to rank.\r</p><br/></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"bg-midnight-mid border-t border-white/10 pt-20 pb-10\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12 mb-16\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-3 group\" href=\"/\"><div class=\"relative w-8 h-8 overflow-hidden\"><img alt=\"Hephzibah Media Logo\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-contain group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2FHephzibah%20Media%20Logo.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2FHephzibah%20Media%20Logo.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2FHephzibah%20Media%20Logo.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2FHephzibah%20Media%20Logo.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2FHephzibah%20Media%20Logo.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2FHephzibah%20Media%20Logo.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2FHephzibah%20Media%20Logo.png&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 204