 max-w-4xl\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h1\",null,{\"className\":\"text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6\",\"children\":\"Untitled\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-gold mb-10\",\"children\":\"$undefined\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"---\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"title: \\\"Print Marketing Still Works in Nigeria: How to Use Banners, Flyers & Business Cards\\\"\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"2\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"date: \\\"2025-01-15T00:00:00Z\\\"\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"3\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"description: \\\"Print isn't dead in Nigeria. Learn how to strategically use flyers, banners, and cards to complement your digital marketing.\\\"\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"4\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"---\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"5\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"6\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"Hephzibah Media\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"7\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"8\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      - [Services](index.html#services)\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"9\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"10\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      - [About](about.html)\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"11\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"12\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      - [Landing Pages](landing-pages-sales-funnels.html)\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"13\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"14\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      - [Training](training.html)\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"15\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"16\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      - [Get a Quote](contact.html\\\" class=\\\"nav-cta)\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"17\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"18\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"19\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"20\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"21\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"22\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"23\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"24\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      Print Marketing · 7 min read\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"25\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      # Print Marketing Still Works in Nigeria: 2025 Guide\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"26\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"27\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      By Hephzibah Media Team · Published January 5, 2025\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"28\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      Everyone talks about 'going digital.' But in Nigeria, print is still incredibly effective  especially when combined with digital. A high-quality business card at a networking event opens doors Google Ads can't. A branded banner at a trade show generates qualified foot traffic. Here's the strategic print playbook for 2025.\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"29\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"30\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"31\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"32\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"33\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"34\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      ## Business Cards: Still Your Best Networking Tool\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"35\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"36\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"37\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"A premium business card (embossed, foil-stamped, specialty paper) positions you as professional and established. It stays on a prospect's desk for months. Cost: ?515 per card. Return: One client contract pays for 10,000 cards. Recommendation: 500 cards every 3 months.\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"38\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"39\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      ## Flyers: Targeted Distribution Beats Broadcast\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"40\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"41\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"42\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"Don't print 10,000 flyers and hope. Instead: 500 flyers, hand-distributed at three high-traffic locations (office parks, malls, events) by your sales team. Include a QR code linking to a landing page  track clicks to measure ROI. Cost: ?50100 per flyer. Conversion: 25% is excellent for flyer campaigns.\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"43\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"44\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      ## Banners at Trade Shows & Events\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"45\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"46\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"47\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"A trade show booth with a compelling banner, product samples, and a clear CTA ('Scan to get 20% off') generates 1020 leads per day. Cost: ?20K50K for the banner. Value: One converted lead from an event is worth ?500K+. Attend 23 high-quality events yearly.\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"48\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"49\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      ## Large Format Printing for Visibility\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"50\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"51\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"52\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"A billboard for your agency costs ?200K500K monthly in high-traffic areas (Lekki, VI, GRA Ikeja). It's expensive, but if your CAC (customer acquisition cost) is below ?50K, a billboard that generates 1015 leads monthly pays for itself. Best for services (real estate, education, fintech).\\r\"}],\"$L1e\",\"$L1f\",\"$L20\",\"$L21\",\"$L22\",\"$L23\",\"$L24\",\"$L25\",\"$L26\",\"$L27\",\"$L28\",\"$L29\",\"$L2a\",\"$L2b\",\"$L2c\",\"$L2d\",\"$L2e\",\"$L2f\",\"$L30\",\"$L31\",\"$L32\",\"$L33\",\"$L34\",\"$L35\",\"$L36\",\"$L37\",\"$L38\",\"$L39\",\"$L3a\",\"$L3b\",\"$L3c\",\"$L3d\",\"$L3e\",\"$L3f\",\"$L40\",\"$L41\",\"$L42\",\"$L43\",\"$L44\",\"$L45\",\"$L46\",\"$L47\",\"$L48\",\"$L49\",\"$L4a\",\"$L4b\",\"$L4c\",\"$L4d\",\"$L4e\",\"$L4f\",\"$L50\",\"$L51\",\"$L52\",\"$L53\",\"$L54\",\"$L55\",\"$L56\",\"$L57\",\"$L58\",\"$L59\",\"$L5a\",\"$L5b\",\"$L5c\",\"$L5d\",\"$L5e\",\"$L5f\",\"$L60\",\"$L61\",\"$L62\",\"$L63\",\"$L64\",\"$L65\",\"$L66\",\"$L67\",\"$L68\",\"$L69\"]}]]}]\n1e:[\"$\",\"br\",\"53\",{}]\n1f:[\"$\",\"p\",\"54\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      ## Packaging as Marketing\\r\"}]\n20:[\"$\",\"br\",\"55\",{}]\n21:[\"$\",\"br\",\"56\",{}]\n22:[\"$\",\"p\",\"57\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"A branded box, tissue paper, or thank-you card in your order transforms a transaction into an experience. Customers photograph it for Instagram. Cost: ?100300 per order. Impact: Word-of-mouth multiplier of 23×.\\r\"}]\n23:[\"$\",\"br\",\"58\",{}]\n24:[\"$\",\"p\",\"59\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      ## The Print + Digital Combo\\r\"}]\n25:[\"$\",\"br\",\"60\",{}]\n26:[\"$\",\"br\",\"61\",{}]\n27:[\"$\",\"p\",\"62\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"QR codes on every print piece. Flyers link to a landing page. Banners include a unique promo code. Business cards have a QR to your LinkedIn. Print gets attention; digital captures the lead. Together, they outperform either channel alone.\\r\"}]\n28:[\"$\",\"br\",\"63\",{}]\n29:[\"$\",\"br\",\"64\",{}]\n2a:[\"$\",\"br\",\"65\",{}]\n2b:[\"$\",\"br\",\"66\",{}]\n2c:[\"$\",\"br\",\"67\",{}]\n2d:[\"$\",\"p\",\"68\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"    ## Ready for Growth?\\r\"}]\n2e:[\"$\",\"br\",\"69\",{}]\n2f:[\"$\",\"br\",\"70\",{}]\n30:[\"$\",\"p\",\"71\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"Let our team audit your current marketing strategy and show you exactly what's holding you back.\\r\"}]\n31:[\"$\",\"br\",\"72\",{}]\n32:[\"$\",\"p\",\"73\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"    [Start Your Free Audit](contact.html\\\" class=\\\"btn-primary)\\r\"}]\n33:[\"$\",\"br\",\"74\",{}]\n34:[\"$\",\"br\",\"75\",{}]\n35:[\"$\",\"br\",\"76\",{}]\n36:[\"$\",\"br\",\"77\",{}]\n37:[\"$\",\"br\",\"78\",{}]\n38:[\"$\",\"p\",\"79\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"        Hephzibah Media\\r\"}]\n39:[\"$\",\"br\",\"80\",{}]\n3a:[\"$\",\"p\",\"81\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"Nigeria's premium Digital Marketing, Tech & Print Agency. Building brands that dominate from Ogere, Ogun State.\\r\"}]\n3b:[\"$\",\"br\",\"82\",{}]\n3c:[\"$\",\"p\",\"83\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"        Old Ode Road, Along Ogere Tollgate, Ogere, Nigeria\\r\"}]\n3d:[\"$\",\"br\",\"84\",{}]\n3e:[\"$\",\"br\",\"85\",{}]\n3f:[\"$\",\"p\",\"86\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"        Services\\r\"}]\n40:[\"$\",\"br\",\"87\",{}]\n41:[\"$\",\"p\",\"88\",{\"cl