s can't. A branded banner at a trade show generates qualified foot traffic. Here's the strategic print playbook for 2025.\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"29\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"30\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"31\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"32\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"33\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"34\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      ## Business Cards: Still Your Best Networking Tool\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"35\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"36\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"37\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"A premium business card (embossed, foil-stamped, specialty paper) positions you as professional and established. It stays on a prospect's desk for months. Cost: ?515 per card. Return: One client contract pays for 10,000 cards. Recommendation: 500 cards every 3 months.\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"38\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"39\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      ## Flyers: Targeted Distribution Beats Broadcast\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"40\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"41\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"42\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"Don't print 10,000 flyers and hope. Instead: 500 flyers, hand-distributed at three high-traffic locations (office parks, malls, events) by your sales team. Include a QR code linking to a landing page  track clicks to measure ROI. Cost: ?50100 per flyer. Conversion: 25% is excellent for flyer campaigns.\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"43\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"44\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      ## Banners at Trade Shows & Events\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"45\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"46\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"47\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"A trade show booth with a compelling banner, product samples, and a clear CTA ('Scan to get 20% off') generates 1020 leads per day. Cost: ?20K50K for the banner. Value: One converted lead from an event is worth ?500K+. Attend 23 high-quality events yearly.\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"48\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"49\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      ## Large Format Printing for Visibility\\r\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"50\",{}],[\"$\",\"br\",\"51\",{}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"52\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"A billboard for your agency costs ?200K500K monthly in high-traffic areas (Lekki, VI, GRA Ikeja). It's expensive, but if your CAC (customer acquisition cost) is below ?50K, a billboard that generates 1015 leads monthly pays for itself. Best for services (real estate, education, fintech).\\r\"}],\"$L2\",\"$L3\",\"$L4\",\"$L5\",\"$L6\",\"$L7\",\"$L8\",\"$L9\",\"$La\",\"$Lb\",\"$Lc\",\"$Ld\",\"$Le\",\"$Lf\",\"$L10\",\"$L11\",\"$L12\",\"$L13\",\"$L14\",\"$L15\",\"$L16\",\"$L17\",\"$L18\",\"$L19\",\"$L1a\",\"$L1b\",\"$L1c\",\"$L1d\",\"$L1e\",\"$L1f\",\"$L20\",\"$L21\",\"$L22\",\"$L23\",\"$L24\",\"$L25\",\"$L26\",\"$L27\",\"$L28\",\"$L29\",\"$L2a\",\"$L2b\",\"$L2c\",\"$L2d\",\"$L2e\",\"$L2f\",\"$L30\",\"$L31\",\"$L32\",\"$L33\",\"$L34\",\"$L35\",\"$L36\",\"$L37\",\"$L38\",\"$L39\",\"$L3a\",\"$L3b\",\"$L3c\",\"$L3d\",\"$L3e\",\"$L3f\",\"$L40\",\"$L41\",\"$L42\",\"$L43\",\"$L44\",\"$L45\",\"$L46\",\"$L47\",\"$L48\",\"$L49\",\"$L4a\",\"$L4b\",\"$L4c\",\"$L4d\"]}]]}],null,\"$L4e\"]}],\"isPartial\":false,\"staleTime\":300,\"varyParams\":null,\"buildId\":\"i9Cf0qMmt9f6Hl-9FDnLU\"}\n2:[\"$\",\"br\",\"53\",{}]\n3:[\"$\",\"p\",\"54\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      ## Packaging as Marketing\\r\"}]\n4:[\"$\",\"br\",\"55\",{}]\n5:[\"$\",\"br\",\"56\",{}]\n6:[\"$\",\"p\",\"57\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"A branded box, tissue paper, or thank-you card in your order transforms a transaction into an experience. Customers photograph it for Instagram. Cost: ?100300 per order. Impact: Word-of-mouth multiplier of 23×.\\r\"}]\n7:[\"$\",\"br\",\"58\",{}]\n8:[\"$\",\"p\",\"59\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"      ## The Print + Digital Combo\\r\"}]\n9:[\"$\",\"br\",\"60\",{}]\na:[\"$\",\"br\",\"61\",{}]\nb:[\"$\",\"p\",\"62\",{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"QR codes on every print piece. Flyers link to a landing page. Banners include a unique promo code. Business c